reviewText: 4 stars cuz it kept me on the edge of my seat. Dont think much about the movie itself.
Love this movie it's a lot of fun.

Blood Diner was one of those movies that was always visible at the local video store but I just never got around to seeing. The VHS cover always intrigued me.

 Anyway last night I saw it and really wished I hadn't. It was one of the worst 80's horror movies I've ever seen. The acting, the plot, the gore the lot. Oh well at least I've finally seen Blood Diner now.
